01:50:26.895 --> 01:50:28.828
Not guilty!

01:50:28.830 --> 01:50:30.597
Not guilty.

01:50:30.599 --> 01:50:33.166
Not guilty!
Sam!

01:50:33.168 --> 01:50:34.701
